

## 1. Project Title

**Event Registration Portal**

## 2. Topic Abstract

The Event Registration Portal is a web-based application designed to simplify the process of event management and participant registration. The system allows users to view available events, register online, and receive confirmation instantly. Administrators can create, update, and delete event details, manage participant information, and monitor registrations efficiently.

The project aims to reduce manual work, improve data accuracy, and provide a user-friendly platform for organizing events in colleges, companies, and organizations.

